
                       geant4-10-02-ref-08
                       ===================

Major development/fixes included since the last development tag are:

 o Fix to preserve same build optimisation settings of libraries installation
   when building applications/examples in single-mode installation for CMake.
 o Reviewd implementation of CalculateExtent() in G4Box and G4Tubs to make use
   of G4BoundingEnvelope.
 o Adopting G4StatDouble for scoring.
 o Extended default upper energy limits from 10 TeV to 100 TeV for EM energy
   loss process. Added new methods and UI commands to define optional EM
   physics per geometrical region.
 o Enabled reading of floating levels and entry as unique nuclides into decay
   tables in radioactive_decay module.
 o Updated data set G4RadioActiveDecay-5.0.

---------- Reference-tag 'Release Notes' -----------

(*)  Fixes included in release 10.2.p03

Summarised, the list of changes is the following:

cmake                                            cmake-V10-02-20
-----
- Fix to preserve same build optimisation settings of libraries installation
  when building applications/examples.
  Currently applicable only for single-mode installation.
- Updated to data set G4RadioActiveDecay-5.0.

analysis                                         analysis-V10-02-09
--------
- Fixed writing of CSV profiles.

event                                            event-V10-02-08
-----
- Changed the way of deleting G4PrimaryVertex objects to avoid stack         (*)
  overflow for very large number of primary vertices.

geometry
--------
- management (geommng-V10-02-18):
  o G4BoundingEnvelope: fixed bug in construction of voxel edges.
- navigation (geomnav-V10-02-12):                                            (*)
  o G4PropagatorInField: fix to pass accuracy values to Intersection Locator
    after re-evaluating epsilon.
  o More diagnostics in G4VERBOSE mode in G4Navigator::GetGlobalExitNormal().
- solids/Boolean (geom-bool-V10-02-10):
  o G4SubtractionSolid: directly return previously computed distance in      (*)
    DistanceToIn(p,v) if no progress is made (zero step).
- solids/CSG (geom-csg-V10-02-06):
  o Re-implemented CalculateExtent() of G4Box and G4Tubs to make use of
    G4BoundingEnvelope. Implemented bounding-box in G4Tubs to take into
    consideration cuts in phi and construction of bounding envelope for
    rotated cases.
    Removed no-longer used method CreateRotatedVertices() implementations.

global                                           global-V10-02-26
------
- G4StatDouble: fixed computation of RMS and added new constructor.          (*)
- G4UnitsTable: added IsUnitDefined() method, checking existance of a unit
  in the table. Addressing problem report #1880.

graphics_reps                                    greps-V10-02-07
-------------
- G4VGraphicsScene: build-in scorer now uses G4TMitsMap<G4StatDouble> instead
  of G4THitsMap<G4double>. Added pure virtual methods AddSolid() for G4Orb and
  G4Ellipsoid.

particles                                        particles-V10-02-24
---------
- Changed the way of deleting G4PrimaryVertex and G4PrimaryParticle objects  (*)
  to avoid stack overflow for very large number of primary vertices or primary
  particles.
- Introduced new class G4NucleiPropertiesTableAME12, used by default in
  G4NucleiProperties.

physics_lists
-------------
- constructors/electromagnetic (phys-ctor-em-V10-02-27)
  o G4EmModelActivator: added configuration of EM physics per geometrical
    region via UI commands.
  o G4EmLivermorePhysics, G4EmPenelopePhysics, G4EmStandardPhysicsGS,
    G4EmLivermorePolarizedPhysics, G4EmStandardPhysicsWVI: use same style for
    names as for EM physics constructors.
- constructors/hadron_inelastic (phys-ctor-hinelastic-V10-02-03)
  o G4HadronPhysicsQBBC: use de-excitation for the Bertini cascade.

processes/electromagnetic/standard               emstand-V10-02-28
----------------------------------
- Rolled back G4UniversalFluctuation to release 10.3-beta.

processes/electromagnetic/utils                  emutils-V10-02-31
-------------------------------
- G4EmParameters, G4VEmProcess, G4VEnergyLossProcess: extended default upper
  energy limits from 10 TeV to 100 TeV; bins per decade unchanged.
- G4EmParameters, G4EmParametersMessenger: added new methods and UI command
  to define optional EM physics per geometrical region.
  Added interface and UI command to enable thread safe built-in Birks
  saturation corrections; added access to G4EmSaturation, set by default 
  Gaussian nuclear form-factor.
- G4EmSaturation: make it thread safe, added data for G4_PbWO4; fixed data
  for G4_lAr, according to recent report from ATLAS.
  Run-time methods are now "const". 
- G4LossTableManager: changed initialisation of G4EmSaturation.
- G4AtomicDeexcitation, G4EmParameters, G4EmParametersMessenger: improved
  initialisation per region.

processes/hadronic
------------------
- models/lend (hadr-lend-V10-02-04)                                          (*)
  o Fixed to use G4Random.
- models/parton_string/hadronization (had-hadronization-V10-02-13)
  o G4ExcitedStringDecay: bug-fix in FragmentStrings() method (access
    to the first element of an empty vector.
- models/radioactive_decay (radioactive_decay-V10-02-10)
  o G4RadioactiveDecay: enabled reading of floating levels and entry as unique 
    nuclides into decay tables.
  o Allow  nuclides with floating levels to decay in G4RadioactiveDecay and all
    specific decay channel classes.
  o G4NuclearDecay: added Get() method for floating level.
  o Removed obsolete class G4NuclearDecayChannel and all classes based on it:
    G4AlphaDecayChannel, G4BetaMinusDecayChannel, G4BetaPlusDecayChannel,
    G4ITDecayChannel, G4KshellECDecayChannel, G4LshellECDecayChannel,
    G4MshellECDecayChannel and G4ProtonDecayChannel.
  o Requires new data-set G4RadioactiveDecay-5.0.

run                                              run-V10-02-23
---
- Added new dependency to global/HEPNumerics in build scripts.

visualization                                    vis-V10-02-13
-------------
- Built-in scorer now uses G4THitsMap<G4StatDouble> instead of
  G4THitsMap<G4double>.
- Fixed G4Orb and G4Ellipsoid hiding warnings
- management:
  o Implemented auxiliary edge drawing for G4Orb, G4Sphere, G4Torus and
    G4Ellipsoid, unless otherwise specified.
- modeling:
  o Updated according to changes in graphics_reps module.
- Tree (vistree-V10-02-01):
  o Improved printing and guidance.

data sets:
---------
- G4RadioactiveDecay-5.0:
  o Added floating levels (X, Y, Z, etc.).

