- advanced/microbeam (microbeam-V10-02-01)
  o Updated analysis script.
- extended/electromagnetic/TestEm0 (testem0-V10-02-04)
  o RunAction: fixed computation of Tmax.
  o PhysicsList: removed hardcoded enabling of CSDA range table
  o Added UI commands enabling print of list of EM parameters and enabling
    computation of CSDA range in TestEm0.in input macro.
- extended/electromagnetic/TestEm8 (testem8-V10-02-03)
  o Run: fixed RMS computation by G4StatDouble.
- extended/electromagnetic/TestEm9 (testem9-V10-02-01)
  o Added validation of EM physics per geometrical region in TestEm9.in macro.
- extended/electromagnetic/TestEm17 (testem17-V10-02-02)
  o Removed obsolete EventAction, EventActionMessenger classes.
- extended/hadronic/Hadr01 (exhadr01-V10-02-00)
