- extended/runAndEvent/RE03 (exampleRE03-V10-02-00)
  o Migrated to use G4THitsMap<G4StatDouble>.

tests                                            tests-V10-02-08
-----
- Updated reference outputs and tools.
- tests/test44 (test44-V10-02-03)
  o Cleanup of scripts.
- tests/test65 (test65-V10-02-05)
  o Add MD5 hash value to CMake script.
- tests/test202 (test202-V10-02-01)
  o Removed specification of auxiliary edge drawing for G4Sphere and G4Orb.
